<h2 id="çƒé¢èª¿å’Œé–¢æ•°ã®åŠ æ³•å®šç†">çƒé¢èª¿å’Œé–¢æ•°ã®åŠ æ³•å®šç†</h2>

<p>\(\mathbf{x}=(\sin \theta \cos \varphi, \sin \theta \sin \varphi, \cos \theta), \mathbf{y}=(\sin \theta' \cos \varphi', \sin \theta' \sin \varphi', \cos \theta')\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€åŠå¾„1ã®çƒé¢ä¸Šã®2ç‚¹ã«ã¤ã„ã¦ã€ãã®å†…ç©ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\mathbf{x} \cdot \mathbf{y} 
= \sin \theta \sin \theta' \cos(\varphi-\varphi') + \cos \theta \cos \theta' 
\equiv \cos \alpha\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§ã“ã®\(\cos \alpha\)ã‚’ç”¨ã„ãŸLegendreé–¢æ•°\(P_\ell\)ã‚’</p>

\[P_\ell (\cos \alpha) 
= \sum_{m=-\ell}^\ell b_m (\theta', \varphi') Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi) \tag{5}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«çƒé¢èª¿å’Œé–¢æ•°ã§å±•é–‹ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ã¨ãä¿‚æ•°\(b_m\)ã«\(\theta', \varphi'\)ã®ä¾å­˜æ€§ã‚’æŠ¼ã—ä»˜ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚ç›´äº¤æ€§ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[b_m (\theta', \varphi') 
= \int_0^\pi d\theta \int_0^{2\pi} d\varphi P_\ell (\cos \gamma) Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi)^\ast \sin \theta \tag{6}\]

<p>ã¨æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(\gamma\)ã¯é©å½“ãªè§’åº¦ã§ã™ã€‚åŒæ§˜ã«</p>

\[Y_\ell^{m \ast} 
= \sum_{m'=-\ell}^\ell B_{mm'}Y_\ell^{m'} (\alpha, \beta) \tag{7}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«\(Y_\ell^{m\ast}\)ã‚’\(Y_\ell^{m'}(\alpha, \beta)\)ã§å±•é–‹ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚\(\beta\)ã‚‚é©å½“ãªè§’åº¦ã§ã™ã€‚ã‚„ã¯ã‚Šç›´äº¤æ€§ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[B_{mm'} 
= \int_{4\pi} Y_\ell^{m} (\theta, \varphi)^\ast Y_\ell^{m'}(\alpha, \beta)^\ast d\Omega_{\alpha, \beta}\]

<p>ã¨æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚ç‰¹ã«\(m'=0\)ã®ã¨ã</p>

\[B_{m0} 
= \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} \int_{4\pi} Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi)^\ast P_\ell^0 (\cos \alpha) d\Omega_{\alpha, \beta}
= \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} \int_{4\pi} Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi)^\ast P_\ell (\cos \alpha) d\Omega_{\alpha, \beta}\]

<p>ã“ã®ç«‹ä½“è§’ç©åˆ†ã¯\(\alpha, \beta\)ã§è¡Œã†ã“ã¨ã¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ãŒã€å…¨ç«‹ä½“è§’ç©åˆ†ãªã®ã§ã€\(\theta, \varphi\)ã§ã®å…¨ç«‹ä½“è§’ã®ç©åˆ†ã«å¤‰ãˆã¦ã‚‚çµæœã¯åŒã˜ã§ãªã‘ã‚Œã°ãªã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[B_{m0} 
= \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} \int_0^\pi d\theta \int_0^{2\pi} d\varphi Y_\ell^{m \ast} P_\ell (\cos \alpha) \sin \theta 
\underbrace{=}_{(6)} \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} b_m (\theta', \varphi') \tag{8}\]

<p><a href="/math/associated_legendre">Legendreé™ªé–¢æ•°ã®å…ƒã®å®šç¾©</a>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[P_n^m(z)
=(1-z^2)^{m/2} \frac{d^m P_n}{dz^m} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
P_n^m (1) 
= P_n^m(-1) 
= \delta_{m0}\]

<p>ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[Y_\ell^m (0, \beta) 
= (-1)^m \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi} \frac{(\ell-m)!}{(\ell+m)!}} \delta_{m0} e^{im\varphi}\]

<p>(7)å¼ã«\(\alpha=0\)ã‚’ä»£å…¥ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[Y_\ell^m(\theta, \varphi)^\ast 
= \sum_{m=-\ell}^\ell B_{mm'} (-1)^{m'} \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi} \frac{(\ell-m')!}{(\ell+m')!}} \delta_{m' 0} e^{im'\varphi} 
= \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} B_{m0}\]

<p>ãã®å®šç¾©ã‹ã‚‰ã€\(\alpha\)ã¯\(\mathbf{x}, \mathbf{y}\)ã®ãªã™è§’åº¦ã§ã—ãŸã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦\(\alpha=0\)ã¯\(\theta=\theta', \varphi=\varphi'\)ã‚’æ„å‘³ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[Y_\ell^m (\theta', \varphi')^\ast 
= \sqrt{\frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi}} \underbrace{B_{m0}}_{(8)} 
= \frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi} b_m (\theta', \varphi')\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[P_\ell (\cos \alpha) 
= P_\ell (\mathbf{x} \cdot \mathbf{y}) 
\underbrace{=}_{5} \frac{4\pi}{2\ell + 1} \sum_{m=-\ell}^\ell Y_\ell^m (\theta', \varphi')^\ast Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi) \tag{9}\]

<p>ã“ã‚Œã¯ä¸‰è§’é–¢æ•°ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹åŠ æ³•å®šç†\(\cos (\theta - \theta') = \cos \theta' \cos \theta + \sin \theta \sin \theta'\)ã‚’ä¸€èˆ¬åŒ–ã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã¨è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="ã‚¦ãƒ³ã‚¼ãƒ«ãƒˆã®å®šç†">ã‚¦ãƒ³ã‚¼ãƒ«ãƒˆã®å®šç†</h2>

<p>(8)å¼ã«ãŠã„ã¦\(\mathbf{x} = \mathbf{y}\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€\(P_\ell(\mathbf{x}\cdot \mathbf{y}) =P_\ell(1)=1\)ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\sum_{m=-\ell}^\ell Y_\ell^m (\theta', \varphi')^\ast Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi) 
= \frac{2\ell+1}{4\pi} \tag{10}\]

<p>ã¨æ±‚ã¾ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã‚’Unsoldã®å®šç†ã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã¯ä¸‰è§’é–¢æ•°ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹\(\cos^2 \theta + \sin^2 \theta=1\)ã‚’ä¸€èˆ¬åŒ–ã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã¨è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

